01:02:38,722 --> 01:02:40,889
♪ Oh, yeah ho! ♪

1068
01:02:40,891 --> 01:02:43,258
♪ Yow! ♪

1069
01:02:46,130 --> 01:02:48,730
♪ Được rồi. Hey! ♪

1070
01:02:48,732 --> 01:02:51,934
♪ Được rồi ♪
